hadiths[188]{hadithnumber,text}:
1180,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Asamm sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey namaz mein takbeeron key barey mein puchha gaya to unhoney farmaya : takbir ( Allahu-akbar ) kahey jab rukoo kerey. jab sajda kerey. jab sajdey sey sar uthaey aur jab do rakaaton sey khada ho. Hateem ney un sey puchha ke ye baat aap ney kis sey yad rakhi hai? unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam), Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr Raziallahu anhuma sey, phir khamosh ho gaey. Hateem ney kaha : Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ? farmaya : han, Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi."
1181,Hazrat Mutrif bin Abdullah sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ney namaz padhi to wo har jhukney aur uthney key waqt puri takbir kehtey they. Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : yaqinan unhoney mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz yad kara di hai.
1182,Hazrat abu-Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab do rakaaton key baad khadey hotey to « Allahu-akbar » kehtey aur apney dono haath uthatey yahan tak ke unhein apney kandhon key barabar kartey they jaisa ke aap ney namaz shuru kartey waqt kya tha.
1183,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz shuru kartey to rafaul-yadein farmatey aur jab rukoo ka irada farmatey aur jab rukoo sey sar uthatey aur jab do rakaaton key baad khadey hotey to isi tarah kandhon tak apney dono haath uthatey. (yani rafaul-yadein farmatey ).
1184,"Hazrat Sahal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Banu Amr bin Auf (ehale-quba) key darmiyan suleh karwaney tashrif ley gaey. ( Asr ki) namaz ka waqt ho gaya to muazza Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aaya aur kaha ke logon ko ikhatta karen aur imaamat farmaeyn. (namaz shuru hotey hi) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye. aap safon ko cheertey huye pehli saf mein aa khadey huye. logon ney abu-Bakar ko muttala karney key liye taliyan bajana shuru kar din taake unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) (ki tashrif aawrii ) key barey mein muttala karen. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) namaz mein idhar-udhar tawajjoh nahin farmatey they. jab unhoney ziyada hi taliyan bajaain to unki samajh mein aaya ke namaz mein koi mushkil pesh aai hai. unhoney tawajjoh ki to wahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein ishara farmaya ke aap apni haalat mein rahen to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney haath uthaey aur aap key us farman par Allah Taala ki hamd o sana ki, phir ultey paaun peechey hatey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aagey badhey aur namaz padhaai . jab aap namaz sey farigh huye to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : jab mainey tumhein ishara kar diya tha to phir tumhein kis chiz ney namaz padhaaney sey roka? Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kya : abu-Qahaafa key betey ko laaiq aur munasib na tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka Imam banta. phir aap ney logon sey farmaya : kya wajeh hai ke tum ney taliyan bajana shuru kar din, taliyan bajaney ka hukm to aurton key liye hai? jab tumhein namaz mein koi mushkil pesh aaye to « subhan Allah » kaha karo."
1185,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye to hum namaz (key ikhtitaam par salam) mein haath utha rahey they. aap ney farmaya : unhein kya huwa hai ke namaz mein haath utha rahey hain goya ke wo sarkash ghodon ki dumein hain? namaz mein sukoon ikhtiyar karo."
1186,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey namaz padhtey they to haathon sey salam kartey they. aap ney farmaya : unhein kya huwa hai ke haathon sey salam kar rahey hain goya ke wo sarkash ghodon ki dumein hain? kya unhein kafi nahin ke apney haath apni raanon par rakhey rahen aur (zaban sey) keh den : ( السلام علیکم , السلام علیکم )"
1187,"Sahabiye-Rasool Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey guzra jab ke aap namaz padh rahey they. mainey aap ko salam kaha to aap ney mujhey ungli key isharay sey jawab diya."
1188,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) masjide-Quba mein namaz padhney key liye dakhil huye. kuch log aaye, aap ko salam kehney lagey. mainey Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha, kyonkey wo aap key sath they, ke phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kya kartey they, jab aap ko salam kaha jata tha? unhoney farmaya : aap haath sey ishara farmatey they."
1189,"Hazrat Ammaar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko salam kaha jabkey aap namaz mein they to aap ney (isharey sey) jawab diya."
1190,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney kisi kaam sey bheja, main wapis aaya to mainey aap ko namaz ki haalat mein paya. mainey aap ko salam kya, aap ney meri taraf ishara kya. phir aap jab namaz sey farigh huye to mujhey bulaya aur farmaya : tum ney abhi mujhey salam kya tha jab ke main namaz padh raha tha. asal mein aap us waqt mashriq ki taraf ja rahey they."
1191,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ( kisi kaam sey) bheja. main wapis aaya to aap mashriq ya maghrib ki taraf tashrif ley ja rahey they. mainey salam keh diya. aap ney apney haath sey ishara kya. mainey phir salam kaha to aap ney phir haath sey ishara kya. mein chala gaya. ( kuch der baad ) aap ney mujhey aawaz di : aey Jabir ! logon ney bhi aawazen din. Jabir Jabir! main hazir huwa to mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! mainey aap ko salam kaha tha, aap ney jawab nahin diya. aap ney farmaya : main namaz padh raha tha."
1192,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs namaz mein ho to kankariyan na chhuey kyonkey rehmate-Ilahi uski taraf mutawajjeh hoti hai."
1193,"Hazrat Mueqeeb (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar tujhey zarur kankariyon ko humwaar karna padey to eik dafa kar ley ( bar-bar na kar )."
1194,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya wajeh hai, kuch log namaz mein apni nazren aasman ki taraf uthatey hain. phir aap ney uskey barey mein sakht alfaz irshad farmaey, yahan tak ke farmaya : log is kaam sey baaz aa jaeyn warna un ki nazren uchak li jaeyngi."
1195,Hazrat Ubedullah bin Abdullah sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sahaba mein sey eik sahabi ney mujh sey bayan kya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huye suna : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs namaz mein ho to apni nazar aasman ki taraf na uthaey (kahin aisa na ho) ke wo uchak li jaey.
1196,"Hazrat Abu-Zar Raziallahu anhu sey manqul hai, farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz ki haalat mein Allah Taala apney bandey ki taraf mutawajjeh rehta hai jab tak wo idhar udhar na dekhey. jab wo apna munh idhar-udhar karta hai to Allah Taala us sey tawajjoh munqata farma leta hai."
1197,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey namaz mein idhar-udhar dekhney key barey mein sawal kya to aap ney farmaya : ye uchakna hai ke shetan usey namaz sey uchak leta hai.
1198,Hazrat Ash-as ki ye riwayat zyada ki bajaey Abul-Ehwas sey bhi hamen Amr bin Ali ney isi tarah bayan farmaya.
1199,"Hazrat Ash-as ki yehi riwayat Amr bin Ali ney hamen isi tarah bayan farmaai, lekin is mein zyada aur Abul-Ehwas ki bajaey Israel ka wasta zikr kya jab ke Abul-Shaa-Saa ki bajaey Abu-Atiya ka zikr kya."
1200,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke namaz mein idhar-udhar dekhna shetan ki loot-khasoot hai jo wo insan ki namaz ( mein) sey karta hai.
1201,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bimar ho gaey. hamney aap key peechey namaz padhi. aap baithey they aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko aap ki takbir sunatey they. aap ney hamen khadey dekha. aap ney hamen bethney ka ishara farmaya. hum baith gaey aur hamney aap key peechey baith kar namaz padhi. jab aap ney salam phera to farmaya : abhi tum Farsiyon aur Rumiyon jaisa kaam kar rahey they. wo apney baadshaahon key samney khadey rehtey hain jab ke badshah bethey rehtey hain. tum aisey na karo. apney imaamon ki perwi karo. agar wo khadey ho kar namaz padhein to tum bhi khadey ho kar namaz padho aur agar wo baith kar namaz padhein to tum bhi baith kar namaz padho.
1202,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma farmatey hain ke Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz mein daaeyn baaeyn dekh kya kartey they magar apni gardan mod kar pichli taraf nahin kartey they.
1203,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz mein do siyah janwer ( sanp aur bichho ) qatl karney ka hukm diya hai.
1204,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney namaz mein do siyah janwer ( sanp aur bichho ) qatl karney ka hukm diya hai.
1205,Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni nawasi Amama (Raziallahu anha) ko utha kar namaz padh liya kartey they. jab aap sajda kartey to usey utaar detey aur jab khadey hotey to usey utha letey.
1206,Hazrat abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ko jamaat karwa rahey hain aur aap ney Amama binte-Abul-Aas ko apney kandhey par utha rakha hai. jab rukoo farmatey to bachi ko utaar detey aur jab sajdey sey farigh hotey to dobara utha letey.
1207,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey darwaza khatkhataya. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) nafl namaz padh rahey they. darwaza qibley ki janib tha. aap ney thoda sa daeyn ya baeyn chal kar darwaza khol diya aur phir apni namaz ki jagah par wapis chaley gaey.
1208,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : namaz mein (Imam ko mutawajjeh karney key liye) « subhan Allah » kehna mardon key liye hai aur taali bajana aurton key liye hai."
1209,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : « subhan Allah » kehna mardon key liye hai aur taali bajana aurton key liye."
1210,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : « subhan Allah » kehna mardon key liye hai aur taali bajana aurton key liye."
1211,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : « subhan Allah » kehna mardon key liye hai aur taali bajana aurton key liye."
1212,Hazrat Ali Raziallahu anhu bayan kartey hain ke merey liye eik waqt muqarrar tha jab main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa karta tha. jab main aap key paas aata to ijazat talab karta. agar main aap ko namaz ki haalat mein paata to aap khankar detey aur main dakhil ho jata aur agar main aap ko faraaghat mein paata to aap mujhey ijazat inayat farmatey.
1213,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : merey liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas janey key do waqt muqarrar they. eik din ko aur eik raat ko. jab main raat ko aap ki khidmat mein hazir hota to aap khankaar detey.
1214,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key nazdik merey liye khususi martaba o maqam tha jo kisi dusrey ka na tha. main har raat sehri key waqt aap key paas jata aur kehta (Assalamualaik ya Nabi Allah ) agar aap khankartey to main wapis ghar aa jata warna aap key paas ( andar) chala jata tha.
1215,"Hazrat Mutrif apney walid (Hazrat Abdullah bin Shikhkhir (Raziallahu anhu) ) sey bayan kartey hain, unhoney farmaya : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya jab ke aap namaz padh rahey they aur aap key seeney sey aisi aawaz aa rahi thi jaisey handiya ubal rahi ho, yani aap ro rahey they."
1216,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey namaz padh rahey they ke achcha hamney aap ko ye farmatey suna : (أعوذ باللہ منک) main tujh sey Allah ki panah maangta hun. phir aap ney teen dafa farmaya : (العنک بلعنۃ اللہ) main tujh par Allah Taala ki lanat bhejta hun. neez aap ney apna haath aagey badhaya goya ke koi chiz pakad rahey hain. jab aap namaz sey farigh huye to hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! hamney aaj aapko namaz mein aisey alfaz kehtey suna hai jo issey pehley kabhi nahin suney aur hamney aapko dekha ke aap ney apna haath aagey badhaya tha. aap ney farmaya : Allah ka dushman iblees aag ka eik bhadakta huwa shola ley kar aaya tha taake merey chehrey par dal dey to mainey teen dafa kaha : (أعوذ باللہ منک) main tujh sey Allah ki panah maangta hun. phir mainey kaha : (العنک بلعنۃ اللہ) main tujh par Allah ki lanat bhejta hun. lekin wo peechey na hata. teen dafa aisa huwa. aakhir mainey usey pakadney ka irada kya. Allah ki qasam! agar merey bhai Hazrat Suleman (Alaihissalam) alehissalam ney dua na ki hoti to usey sutun sey baandh diya jata aur subh ehal Madina key bachey us sey kheltey."
1217,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz key liye khadey huye. hum bhi aap key sath khadey huye. eik Erabi (dehati) ney doran namaz mein kaha : ( اللھم ! ارحمنی … … … … ) aey Allah ! mujh par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par reham farma aur hamarey ilawa kisi aur par reham na farma. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney salam phera to us Erabi (dehati) sey farmaya : tu ney eik wasee chiz ko tang kar diya. aap ka maqsad tha ke Allah ki rehmat to bahut wasee hai.
1218,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik Erabi (dehati) masjid mein dakhil huwa. us ney do rakatein padhin, phir kehney laga : ( اللھم ! ارحمنی … … … ) aey Allah ! mujh par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par reham farma. hamarey sath kisi aur par reham na farma. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tu ney eik wasee chiz ko tang kar diya."
1219,"Hazrat Muawiya bin Hakam Sulami (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamney jahiliyat abhi taza taza chhodi hai aur Allah Taala ney Islam bheja hai. hum mein sey kuch log badshigooni pakadtey hain. aap ney farmaya : ye eik be haqiqat chiz hai jisey wo apney dilon mein mehsus kartey hain, lihaza ye unhein unkey kaam kaaj sey na rokey. ( mainey kaha : ) aur hum mein sey kuch log kaahinon key paas jatey hain. aap ney farmaya : unkey paas mat jaya karo. mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aur hum mein sey kuch log khat khinchtey hain. aap ney farmaya : nabiyon mein sey eik Nabi ( alehissalam ) khat khincha kartey they. jo shakhs unkey mutabiq khat kheenchey, wo to theek hai (aur baqi ghalat). Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke eik baar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padh raha tha ke eik aadmi ko chheenk aa gaee. mainey (Yarhamkullah) Allah Taala tujh par reham farmaai padhi. keh diya. log mujhey ghoor-ghoor kar dekhney lagey. mainey ( pareshan ho kar) kaha : haaye ! meri maa mujhey gum karey ! ( yani main mar jaaun) tumhein kya huwa hai ke tum mujhey is tarah dekh rahey ho? log (be-basi sey) apni raanon par haath maarney lagey (kyonkey wo namaz ki wajeh sey bol nahin saktey they. ) jab mainey mehsus kya ke wo mujhey chup kara rahey hain to aakhir mein chup ho gaya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey farigh huye to mujhey bulaya. merey maa baap aap par fidaa hon! aap ney mujhey maara, na jhidka, na bura bhala kaha. Wallah! mainey aap sey pehley ya baad koi ustaad aap sey ziyada achey andaz mein taalim deney wala nahin dekha. aap ney (shafqat sey) farmaya : hamari is namaz mein logon ki kisi qism ki baat karna jayez aur durust nahin. namaz to sirf tasbeehaat, takbeeraat aur tilawat Quran ka naam hai. Hazrat Muawiya ney kaha : phir eik dafa main apni kuch bakriyan dekhney gaya jinhein meri eik laundi Jabale-Uhad aur jawaaniya ki taraf churaaya karti thi. mainey achi tarah jayeza liya to pata chala ke eik bakri ko bhediya ley gaya hai, main bhi aulade-Adam mein sey eik aadmi tha, mujhey ghussa aa gaya jis tarah logon ko ghussa aata hai. mainey usey thappad maar diya. phir (mujhey nadaamat hui to) main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas gaya aur aap ko sara waqia bataya. aap ney usey meri bahut badi ghalati qarar diya to mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya main usey azad hi na kar dun? aap ney farmaya : usey merey paas bulaao (mein usey laya to) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey puchha : Allah Taala kahan hai? us ney kaha : aasman mein ( yani uper). aap ney farmaya : main kon hun? us ney kaha : aap Allah key Rasool hain. aap ney farmaya : ye momina aurat hai, usey azad kar do."
1220,Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key ( ibtidaai ) daur mein log namaz mein apney sathi sey zarurat ki baat kar letey they yahan tak ke ye aayat utri : حافظوا Ali (Raziallahu anhu) الصلوت و الصلوۃ الوسطی و قوموا للہ قنتینtum sab namazon ki hifazat karo aur khas taur par afzal namaz ki aur Allah key samney farmanbardar ho kar khadey raho. to hamen (is qism ki baaton sey) khamosh rehney ka hukm diya gaya.
1221,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya karta tha jab ke aap namaz padh rahey hotey main aap ko salam kehta to aap mujhey salam ka jawab dey diya kartey they. eik din mein aaya aur aap namaz padh rahey they. mainey aap ko salam kaha, aap ney mujhey jawab nahin diya. jab aap ney salam phera to logon ki taraf ishara kya aur farmaya : (aey logo!) Allah Taala ney namaz key barey main eik naya hukm jari kya hai ke tum (namaz mein) Allah key zikr aur namaz key munasib alfaz key ilawa koi kalam na karo aur Allah Taala key samney aajizi aur sukoon sey khadey raho"
1222,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke hum (pehley pehal) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko (namaz ki haalat mein) salam kar diya kartey they aur aap jawab bhi dey diya kartey they yahan tak ke hum Habsha key ilaqey sey wapis aaye to mainey aap ko (namaz ki haalat mein) salam kya. aap ney mujhey jawab na diya. mujhey to qarib aur door ki sochen aaney lagen (ke jawab na deney ki kya wajeh ho sakti hai?) main beth gaya yahan tak ke jab aap ney namaz puri farmaai to farmaya : bilashuba Allah Taala jo chahta hai, naya hukm jari farmata hai aur Allah Taala ney ye naya hukm jari kya hai ke namaz mein baat cheet na ki jaey."
1223,"Hazrat Abdullah ibne-Buhena (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen do rakatein padhaaein, phir uth khadey huye, bethey nahin. log bhi aap key sath khadey ho gaey. jab aap ney namaz mukammal farma li aur hum aap key salam key intizar mein they to aap ney « Allahu-akbar » keh kar do sajdey kiye jab ke aap salam sey qabl bethey they. phir aap ney salam phera."
1224,"Hazrat Abdullah ibne-Buhena sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz mein (do rakaaton key baad) khadey ho gaey, halanke aap ney bethna tha to aap ney (aakhir mein) salam sey pehley bethey bethey do sajdey kiye."
1225,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen Zohar aur Asr mein sey koi eik namaz padhaai. lekin mein bhool gaya ke wo kon si thi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen do rakatein padha kar salam pher diya. phir aap masjid mein rakhi hui eik lakdi ki taraf gaey aur apna haath is par rakh liya. yun lagta tha jaisey aap ghussey mein hon. kuch jald baaz log masjid key darwazon sey nikal bhi gaey aur kehney lagey : namaz kam ho gaee. logon ( namaaziyon ) main abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma bhi shamil they magar aap sey (us masley mein) baat cheet karney sey wo bhi darey rahey. logon main eik lambey haathon wala shakhs tha jisey zul-yadain (lambey haathon wala) kaha jata tha, us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! aap bhool gaey ya namaz kam ho qaee? aap ney farmaya : main bhoola hun na namaz kam hui hai. (zul-yadain ney kaha : eik kaam to zarur huwa hai.) aap ney (logon sey) puchha : kya baat isi tarah hai jaisey zul-yadain kehta hai? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap (musalley par) tashrif laye aur jo namaz baqi reh gaee thi, padhaai, phir salam phera aur « Allahu-akbar » kaha aur aam sajdey ki tarah ya ussey kuch lamba sajda kya, phir sar uthaya aur «Allahu-akbar» kaha, phir « Allahu-akbar » keh kar doosra sajda kya, aam sajdey ki tarah ya us sey kuch lamba, phir sar uthaya aur « Allahu-akbar » kaha."
1226,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai (eik dafa) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney do Rakaton par salam pher diya to zul-yadain ney aap sey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! kya namaz kam ho gaee ya aap bhool gaey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kya zul-yadain sahih kehta hai? logon ney kaha : ji haan. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthey aur do rakatein mazeed padhaain, phir salam phera. phir « Allahu-akbar » keh kar apney aam sajdey ki tarah ya us sey lamba sajda kya, phir sar uthaya, phir apney aam sajdey ki tarah ya us sey kuch lamba sajda farmaya, phir sar uthaya ."
1227,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen Asr ki namaz padhaai aur do rakaaton par salam pher diya. zul-yadain uth khadey huye aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya namaz kam ho gaee ya aap bhool gaey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : kuch bhi nahin huwa. unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kuch to huwa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : kya zul-yadain ney durust kaha hai? logon ney kaha : ji haan. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney baqi bachi namaz mukammal ki, phir salam pherney key baad bethey bethey do sajdey kiye."
1228,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz ki do rakatein padha kar salam pher diya. logon ney kaha : kya namaz kam ho qaee? aap uthey aur do rakatein mazeed padhin, phir salam phera, phir do sajdey kiye."
1229,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik din namaz padhi aur do rakaaton par salam pher diya aur uth kar chaley gaey to Zu-Shumalain (Raziallahu anhu) aap ko ja kar miley aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya namaz kam ho gaee ya aap bhool gaey ? aap ney farmaya : namaz kam hui hai na main bhoola hun. us ney kaha : kyon nahin (kuch to huwa hai.) qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko haq key sath bheja hai ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (logon sey mukhatib ho kar) farmaya : kya zul-yadain durust keh raha hai? logon ney kaha : haan. to aap ney logon ko do rakatein mazid padhaain.
1230,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhool gaey aur do rakaaton par salam pher diya to Zu-Shumalain ney aap sey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! kya namaz kam ho gaee ya aap bhool gaey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon sey puchha : kya zul-yadain durust keh raha hai? unhoney kaha : haan. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye aur namaz mukammal farmaai."
1231,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ya Asr ki namaz padhaai aur do rakaaton key baad salam pher diya aur uth kar chal diye to Zu-Shumalain bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ney aap sey kaha : kya namaz kam ho gaee ya aap bhool gaey? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya, zul-yadain kya kehta hai? unhoney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! sach kehta hai. aap ney phir wo do rakatein mukammal farmaain jo reh gaee thin."
1232,"Hazrat abu-Bakar bin Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Abu-Hasma ney ibne-Shahab ko bataya ke mujhey ye khabar pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney do rakatein padhin (aur salam pher diya ) to Zu-Shumalain ney aap sey guzarish ki. ( baqi riwayat hasbe-saabiq hai) Hazrat ibne-Shahab Zohri bayan kartey hain ke mujhey ye riwayat Hazrat Saeed bin Musaiyab ney Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bayan farmaai, neez mujhey ye riwayat Hazrat abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman, abu-Bakar bin Abdur-Rehman bin Haris aur Ubedullah bin Abdullah ney bhi bayan farmaey."
1233,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney us din na salam sey pehley sajdey kiye na baad mein."
1234,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney zul-yadain waley waqia key din salam key baad do sajdey kiye."
1235,"(Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain : ) hamen ye riwayat Amr bin Suwad bin Aswad ney ibne-Wahab sey, unhoney Amr bin Haris sey, unhoney (قتادہ an محمد بن سیرین an أبی ھریرۃ an رسول اللہ ﷺ ) ki sanad sey bhi isi tarah bayan farmaai."
1236,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney sahw key (us) waqiey mein salam key baad sajdey kiye.
1237,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney unhein namaz padhaai. aap ko sahw (bhool) ho gaya. aap ney do sajdey kiye, phir salam phera."
1238,Hazrat Imran bin Husein (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (eik dafa) Asr ki namaz mein teen rakaat par salam pher diya. phir apney ghar mein dakhil ho gaey. eik aadmi aap ki taraf badha. uska naam kharbaaq tha. us ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! namaz kam ho qaee? aap ghussey mein apni ooper wali chadar ghasit-tey huye bahar nikley aur farmaya : kya ye durust kehta hai? logon ney kaha : haan. aap musalley par khadey huye aur reh janey wali rakat padhaai. phir salam pheraa. phir saho key do sajdey kiye. phir salam phera.
1239,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko apni namaz mein shak pad jaey to wo shak door karey aur yaqin par buniyad rakhey (yani yaqin key mutabiq namaz jari rakhey) jab usey namaz mukammal honey ka yaqin ho jaey to bethey bethey do sajdey kerey. agar usney paanch (rakaat) padhi hongi to ye do sajdey uski namaz ko juft bana dengey. aur agar us ney chaar (rakaat) padhi hongi to ye do sajdey shetan ko zaleel karney ka sabab banengey."
1240,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko pata na chaley ke us ney teen (rakaat) padhi hain ya chaar? to wo eik rakat mazeed padh kar bethey bethey do sajdey kerey. agar us ney paanch (rakaat) padhi hongi to ye sajdey uski namaz ko juft bana dengey aur agar chaar padhi hain to ye shetan ki zillat ka sabab hongey."
1241,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko apni namaz mein shak pad jaey to usey sahih soorate-hal janney ki koshish kerni chahiye, phir wo apni namaz mukammal kerey. phir do sajdey kerey. (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) farmatey hain : ) main us riwayat key baaz alfaz (apney ustaad girami sey) is tarah nahin samajh saka jis tarah meri khahish thi."
1242,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey kisi ko apni namaz mein shak pad jaey to wo sahih baat janney ki koshish karey aur farigh honey key baad do sajdey kerey."
1243,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik namaz padhi jis mein aap sey ziyadti ya kami ho gaee. jab aap ney salam phera to aap sey puchha gaya : kya namaz key barey mein koi naya hukm aa gaya hai? aap ney farmaya : agar namaz key barey mein koi naya hukm aaya hota to main tumhein bata deta. lekin main bhi eik insan hun, jis tarah tum bhool jatey ho, main bhi bhool jata hun. jis aadmi ko bhi apni namaz mein shak pad jaey to wo dekhey kon si baat sehat key ziyada qarib hai. phir uskey mutabiq apni namaz mukammal kerey. phir salam pherey aur (sahw key) do sajdey kerey."
1244,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney koi namaz padhi. is mein aap sey ziyadti ya kami ho gaee. jab aap ney salam phera to hamney kaha : aey Allah key Nabi ! kya namaz mein koi naya hukm aa gaya hai? aap ney farmaya : kya huwa? hamney aap sey puri baat zikr ki. aap ney apna paaun moda aur qibley ki taraf munh kya aur sahw key do sajdey kiye. phir hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : agar namaz key barey mein koi naya hukm aa jata to main tumhein batla deta. phir farmaya : main bhi eik insan hun, bhool sakta hun jis tarah tum bhool jatey ho, lihaza jis aadmi ko apni namaz mein shak pad jaey, wo sahih soorate-haal janney ki koshish kerey. phir salam pher dey. phir saho key do sajdey kerey."
1245,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki namaz padhaai (aap sey eik rakat zayed padhi qaee) phir aap ney apna chehra logon ki taraf farmaya to logon ney kaha : kya namaz mein koi tabdili aa gaee hai? aap ney farmaya : kya huwa? to unhoney aap ko puri baat batai. aap ney apna paaun moda aur qibley ki taraf munh kya aur do sajdey kiye, phir salam phera, phir unki taraf mutawajjeh ho kar farmaya : main bhi eik insan hun. bhool jata hun jaisey tum bhool jatey ho. jab main bhool jaaun to mujhey yad dila diya karo. agar namaz key barey mein koi tabdili hui hoti to main tumhein bata deta. neez farmaya, jab tum mein sey kisi ko namaz mein weham pad jaey to wo bahut ziyada durust baat malum karey aur uskey hisab sey namaz mukammal kerey. phir do sajdey kerey."
1246,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jisey namaz mein weham ho jaey to wo durust baat talash kerey. phir namaz mukammal karney key baad bethey bethey do sajdey kerey.
1247,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke jisey ( namaz mein) shak ya weham pad jaey to wo durust baat talash kerey. phir do sajdey kerey.
1248,Hazrat Ibrahim Nakhai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke log ( sahaba kiram ) kehtey they : jab namazi ko weham ho jaey to wo durust baat talash kerey. phir do sajdey kerey.
1249,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ko namaz mein shak ho to wo salam pherney key baad do sajdey kerey."
1250,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis aadmi ko namaz mein shak pad jaey to wo salam pherney key baad do sajdey kerey."
1251,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs apni namaz mein shak karey to wo salam pherney key baad do sajdey kerey."
1252,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis shakhs ko apni namaz mein shak ho jaey to wo salam key baad bethey-bethey do sajdey kerey."
1253,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi namaz padhney khada hota hai to shetan aa kar is par uski namaz mushtabah kar deta hai yahan tak ke usey pata nahin chalta ke kitni namaz padhi hai? jab tum mein sey koi shakhs ye soorate-haal paey to (yaqeen key mutabiq namaz mukammal kar key salam pherey aur) bethey-bethey do sajdey kerey."
1254,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab namaz key liye Azan kahi jati hai to shetan gooz maarta huwa bhag jata hai. jab iqaamat puri ho jati hai to wapis aa jata hai yahan tak ke namazi aur uskey dil key darmiyan haael ho jata hai yahan tak ke usey pata nahin chalta ke mainey kitni namaz padhi hai? jab tum mein sey koi shakhs ye soorate-haal dekhey (mehsus kerey) to (namaz yaqin key mutabiq mukammal karney key baad) do sajdey kerey."
1255,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney Zohar ki paanch rakatein padha din. aap sey arz kya gaya : kya namaz mein izafa ho gaya hai? aap ney farmaya : kya huwa? logon ney arz kya : aap ney paanch rakatein padhi hain. aap ney apna paaun moda (yani qibla rukh huye) aur do sajdey kiye.
1256,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen Zohar ki namaz paanch rakatein padha den. logon ney kaha : aap ney paanch padhi hain to aap ney salam pherney key baad bethey bethey do sajdey kiye.
1257,"Ibrahim bin Suwed sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Alqama ney eik dafa paanch rakatein padha din. unhein bataya gaya to wo kehney lagey : mainey to aisa nahin kya. mainey sar key isharay sey kaha : kyon nahin? (aap ney kya hai) wo kehney lagey : aey Aawar! to bhi aisey hi kehta hai? mainey kaha : haan. phir unhoney do sajdey kiye. phir unhoney Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) key wastey sey hadees bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney bhi (eik dafa) paanch rakaat padha di thin. log eik dusrey sey kaana-phoosi karney lagey. unhoney aap sey kaha : kya namaz mein izafa ho gaya hai? aap ney farmaya : nahin. unhoney aap ko bataya to aap ney apney paaun sidhey (qibla rukh) kiye aur do sajdey kiye, phir farmaya : main bhi eik insan hun. jis tarah tum bhooltey ho, mein bhi bhool jata hun."
1258,"Hazrat Shaaby bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Alqama bin Qais apni namaz mein bhool gaey. unkey kalam waghera karney key baad logon ney un sey zikr kya to kehney lagey : aey Aawar! kya aisey hi huwa hai? us ney kaha : ji haan. unhoney apni goth kholi, phir sahw key do sajdey kiye aur kehney lagey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aisey kya tha. (Hadees key raawi) Malik bin mighwal ney kaha : mainey Hazrat hukm bin Utaiba ko farmatey suna ke Alqama ney (ghalati sey) paanch rakatein padh li thin."
1259,Ibrahim bin Suwed sey marwi hai ke Hazrat Alqama ney paanch rakatein padh lin. mainey kaha : aey Abu-Shibl! ( Alqama ki kunniyat hai) aap ney paanch rakatein padhi hain. kehney lagey : aey Aawar! kya haqiqat mein aisa hi hai? phir unhoney saho key do sajdey kiye. phir kehney lagey : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney aisey hi kya tha.
1260,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney pichley pahar ki do namazon (Zohar aur Asr ) main sey koi eik namaz paanch rakat padha di. aap sey puchha gaya : kya namaz mein izafa ho gaya hai? aap ney farmaya : kya huwa? unhoney kaha : aap ney paanch rakatein padhi hain. aap ney farmaya : main bhi eik insan hun. bhool jata hun jis tarah tum bhool jatey ho aur yad rakhta hun jis tarah tum yad rakhtey ho. phir aap ney do sajdey farmaai aur tashrif ley gaey.
1261,Hazrat Yusuf (Umwi) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein Imam bin kar namaz padhaai. wo namaz mein (eik maqam par) khadey ho gaey jabkey unhein bethna chahiye tha. logon ney (Subhan Allah ) kaha lekin wo khadey rahey. phir unhoney namaz puri karney key baad bethey bethey do sajdey kiye. phir member par beth gaey aur farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna : jo shakhs apni namaz mein sey kuch bhool jaey to wo un do sajdon ki tarah sajdey kerey.
1262,Hazrat Abdullah ibne-Buhena sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Zohar ki do rakaaton key baad ( bethney ki bajaey ) sidhey khadey ho gaey. phir (tawajjoh dilaney par bhi) wapis na bethey. jab namaz puri farma li to salam pherney sey pehley bethey bethey do sajdey kiye. har sajdey mein « Allahu-akbar » kehtey they. logon ney bhi aap key sath sajdey kiye. ye us Qaadey ki jagah they jo aap bhool gaey they.
1263,"Hazrat abu-Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) un do rakaaton key baad jin par namaz khatam hoti hai ( tashahud mein bethtey waqt ) apna baayan paaun daain taraf (pindli key nichey sey) bahar nikal letey aur peeth par (zor dey kar) bethtey, phir salam phertey."
1264,Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar Raziallahu anhu bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap jab namaz shuru farmatey jab rukoo farmatey aur jab rukoo sey sar uthatey to rafaul-yadein kartey. aur aap jab bethtey to baain paaun ko bichhatey aur daayan khada kartey aur apna baayan haath apni baain raan par rakhtey aur daayan haath daain raan par rakhtey aur angoothey aur darmiyani ungli sey halqa banatey aur (angusht shahadat sey) ishara farmatey.
1265,"Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha, aap namaz mein bethey aur apna baayan paaun bichaya aur apney dono bazu apni raanon par rakhey aur tashahud padhtey waqt angusht shahadat sey ishara farmaya."
1266,"Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (eik dafa) mainey (apney dil mein) kaha ke Allah ki qism ! main Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ko b-ghaur dekhunga ke aap kaisey namaz padhtey hain? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye, qibley ki taraf munh farmaya aur apney dono haath uthaey yahan tak ke wo kanon key barabar ho gaey. phir aap ney apney baain haath ko daeyn sey pakad liya. jab aap ney rukoo ka irada farmaya to unhein phir isi tarah uthaya aur apney haath apney ghutnon par rakhey, chunanche jab rukoo sey sar uthaya to dono haath phir isi tarah uthaey, phir jab sajda kya to apna sar apney haathon key sath rafaul-yadein wali kefiyat mein rakha. (jahan tak haath uthaey they, wahin tak haath sajdey mein sar key qarib rahey) phir aap beth gaey aur apna baayan paaun bichaya aur apna baayan haath baain raan par rakha aur daeyn kohni ka kinara apni daeyn raan par rakha. do ( chhanguli aur uskey sath wali) ungliyan band kin aur anguthey aur darmiyani ungli sey halqa banaya aur angusht shahadat sey ishara kya."
1267,Hazrat Ali bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma key paas namaz padhi. main kankariyon ko ulat-palat karney laga to mujhey ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehney lagey : kankariyon ko na chhedo kyonkey kankariyon sey khelna shetani harkat hai balke is tarah karo jaisey mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kartey dekha. mainey kaha : aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko kaisey kartey dekha hai? farmaya : aisey. phir ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney apna daayan paaun khada kya aur baain ko bichaya aur apna daayan haath apni daeyn raan par rakha aur baayan haath apni baain raan par rakha aur aap ney shahadat ki ungli sey ishara kya.
1268,Hazrat Ali bin Abdur-Rehman bayan kartey hain ke mujhey Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ney namaz key doran mein kankariyon sey kheltey dekha. jab wo namaz sey farigh huye to unhoney mujhey roka aur farmaya : is tarah karo jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) kartey they. mainey kaha aap kaisey kartey they? unhoney farmaya : aap jab namaz mein bethtey to apni daain hatheli ko (daain) raan par rakhtey aur apni tamam ungliyan band kar letey aur us ungli sey ishara farmatey jo anguthey key sath milti hai aur apna baayan haath apni baain raan par rakhtey.
1269,"Hazrat Waeyl bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey irada kya ke main zarur Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ko b-ghaur dekhunga ke aap kaisey namaz padhtey hain. mainey ghor sey dekha … … phir unhoney bayan kya ke … … … phir aap bethey aur apna baayan paaun bichaya aur apni baain hatheli apni baain raan aur ghutney par rakhi aur apni daeyn kohni ka kinara apni daain raan par rakha. phir (apney daeyn haath ki ) do ungliyan band kin aur (darmiyani ungli aur anguthey sey) halqa banaya. phir apni angushte-shahadat ko uthaya. mainey aap ko dekha, aap usey harkat detey they aur uskey sath dua kartey they. ye riwayat mukhtasar hai."
1270,Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz mein bethtey to apney dono haath apney ghutnon par rakhtey aur angoothey key sath wali ungli uthatey aur uskey sath dua kartey aur baain haath ko khol kar ghutney par rakhtey.
1271,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab dua kartey (tashahud padhtey) to apni ungli sey ishara kartey aur usey harkat nahin detey they. dusri riwayat mein Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye marwi hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aap isi tarah dua kartey they aur aap apna baayan haath (khol kar) apni baain taang par rakhtey they aur is par bojh daltey they.
1272,"Hazrat Numer Khuzaai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko doran namaz mein daayan haath daain raan par rakhey huye dekha. aap apni ungli sey ishara farma rahey they."
1273,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, eik aadmi apni do ungliyon sey ishara kar raha tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik ungli sey ishara kar. eik ungli sey ishara kar."
1274,Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas sey guzrey jabkey main apni kaee ungliyon sey ishara kar raha tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : eik sey kar. eik sey kar. aur aap ney apni ( daeyn haath ki ) angusht shahadat key sath ishara kya.
1275,"Hazrat Numer Khuzaai (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz mein bethey huye dekha. aap ney apna daayan bazu apni daeyn raan par rakha tha aur apni angusht shahadat utha rakhi thi, albatta usey kuch jhukaya huwa tha aur aap tashahud padh rahey they."
1276,Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab tashahud mein bethtey to apni baain hatheli apni baain raan par rakhtey aur (daeyn haath ki) angushte-shahadat sey ishara farmatey. aap ki nazar isharay sey aagey nahin jati thi.
1277,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : log namaz key doran mein dua key waqt aasman ki taraf nazren uthaney sey baaz aa jaeyn warna un ki nazren uchak li jaeyngi."
1278,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke tashahud farz honey sey pehley hum kaha kartey they : (السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) اللہ ، السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) جبریل و میکائیل) Allah par salam ho. Jibril o mekael par salam ho. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aisey na kaho kyonkey Allah azz-w-jall khud salam hai, lekin yun kaho : (التحیات للہ … … … ورسولہ) tamam aadab (ya qouli ibadat) aur tamam duayen aur namazein (ya badani ibadatein) aur pakiza kalimat (ya mali ibadatein) Allah Taala key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ka salam, rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah Taala key nek bandon par bhi salam ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi haqeeqi mabud nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain."
1279,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamen tashahud is tarah sikhatey they jis tarah Quran Majeed ki koi sura sikhatey they.
1280,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : bilashuba Allah Taala khud السلام hai ( lihaza (السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) اللہ) na kaho balke) jab tum mein sey koi (qadey mein) bethey to yun kahey : (التحیات للہ و الصلوات … … … عبدہ و رسولہ) tamam aadaab, sab duayen aur sarey pakizah kalmaat Allah Taala key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par salam ho aur Allah ki rehmat o barkaat nazil hon. hum par aur Allah Taala key nek bandon par salam ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. phir uskey baad wo apni pasand key mutabiq dua kerey."
1281,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke tehqiq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein khutba diya. hamein hamarey tareeqey sikhlaey aur hamarey liye hamari namaz bayan farmaee aur farmaya : jab tum namaz key liye khadey ho to apni saffeen sidhi karo. phir tum mein sey koi shakhs tumhara Imam baney. jab bhi wo (Allahu-Akbar) kahe to tum bhi (Allahu-Akbar) kaho aur jab wo (ولا الضالین) kahe to tum Aameen kaho. Allah Taala tumhari dua qubul farmaeyga. phir jab wo (Allahu-Akbar) kahe aur rukoo karey to tum bhi (Allahu-Akbar) kaho aur rukoo karo. Imam tum sey pehley rukoo ko jata hai aur tum sey pehley sar uthata hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye sabqat us sabqat key muqabley mein hai. aur jab wo (Samiallahu-liman-hamida) kahe to tum (ربنا لک الحمد) kaho. Allah Taala ney apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki zabani farmaya hai ke Allah Taala us shakhs ki baat sunta hai jo uski hamd kerey. phir jab wo (Allahu-Akbar) kahe aur sajda karey to tum bhi (Allahu-Akbar) kaho aur sajda karo. Imam tum sey pehley sajdey ko jata hai aur tum sey pehley sar uthata hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ye sabqat us sabqat key muqabley mein hai. (tumharey aur Imam key sajdey ki miqdaar mein koi farq nahin padey ga.) aur jab Imam qaaedey mein bethey to tumhein yun kehna chahiye : (التحیات الطیبات الصلوات للہ … … … عبدہ ورسولہ),''tamam aadaab, pakizah kalimaat aur duayen Allah Taala key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ki taraf sey salam rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par salam ho aur Allah key tamam nek bandon par bhi. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin aur main gawahi deta hun ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain.''"
1282,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamein is tarah tashahud sikhatey they jaisey hamein Quran Majeed ki sura sikhatey they : (بسم اللہ و باللہ التحیات … … … وأعوذ بہ من النار), ''Allah taala key naam key sath aur Allah Taala ki madad key sath. tamam aadaab, duayen aur pakizah kalimaat Allah Taala key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par Allah Taala ka salam, rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah Taala key tamam nek bandon par salam ho. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi haqeeqi mabood nahin aur Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur Rasool hain. main Allah Taala sey jannat maangta hun aur jahannam sey uski panah chahta hun.'' Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hum nahin jantey ke kisi dusrey raawi ney is riwayat mein Aiman bin Naabil ki muwaafiqat ki ho. Aiman hamarey nazdik moatabar raawi hai, lekin ye riwayat durust nahin. aur tofiq Allah Taala ki madad hi sey milti hai."
1283,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bayan kartey hain ke padhi. tehqiq Allah Taala ney kuchh farishtey muqarrar kar rakhey hain jo zamin mein har waqt chaltey phirtey rehtey hain. wo mujhey meri ummat ki taraf sey salam pahunchatey hain."
1284,"Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik din tashrif laye jab ke aap key chehre anwar par suroor jhalak raha tha. hamney kaha : hum aap key chehre aqdas par khushi key aasaar dekh rahey hain. aap ney farmaya : merey paas eik farishta aaya aur us ney kaha : aey Muhammad ! tehqiq aap ka Rab taala farmata hai : kya aap ko ye baat pasand nahin ke jo shakhs bhi aap par durood padhey ga main is par das dafa rehmat karunga? aur jo bhi aap par salam kahiyega, mein is par das baar salam nazil karunga."
1285,"Hazrat Fazala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney eik aadmi ko namaz mein dua kartey suna jisney na Allah Taala ki hamd bayan ki aur na Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par durood padha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aey namazi ! tu ney jaldi ki hai. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney logon ko dua ka tariqa sikhaya, phir aap ney eik aadmi ko dua kartey huye suna, us ney pehley Allah Taala ki buzurgi aur tareef bayan ki, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par durood padha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ab to dua kar, qubul hogi aur mang tujhey diya jaeyga."
1286,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas Hazrat Saad bin Ibaad (Raziallahu anhu) ki baithak mein tashrif laye. Bashir bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! Allah Taala ney hamein aap par durood padhney ka hukm diya hai. hum aap par kaisey durood padhein? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey yahan tak ke hamney tamanna ki ke wo aap sey na poochhtey. kuchh der key baad aap ney farmaya : tum yun kaho : (للھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد … … … Ali (Raziallahu anhu) آل ابراھیم فی العلمین انک حمید مجید),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur un ki aal par khususi rehmat farma jaisa ke tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par khususi rehmat farmaee. aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par barkate nazil farma jaisa ke tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par tamam jahano mein barkaten nazil farmaeen. yaqinan tu hi qabile tareef aur buzurgi wala hai.''aur salam is tarah padho jaisey tumhein sikhaya gaya hai."
1287,"Hazrat Abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey kaha gaya : hamein hukm diya gaya hai ke hum aap par durood aur salam padhein, salam to hum jaan chukey hain durood kaisey padhein ? aap ney farmaya : tum kaho : (اللھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد … … … Ali (Raziallahu anhu) آل إبراہیم),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par khususi rahmatein farma jaisey tu ney aale Ibrahim par rahmaten farmaeen. aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par barkaten nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par barkaten nazil farmaeen."
1288,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! (tashahud mein) aap par salam padhna to hum jaan chukey hain, lekin durood kaisey padhein? aap ney farmaya : tum yun kaho : (للھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد … … … حمید مجید),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par rahmateyn nazil farma jaisey tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par rahmateyn nazil farmaee hain. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai. aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par barkaten nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par barkaten nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai. (raawi) ibne Abi Lailaa ney kaha : hum sath hi ye bhi kehtey they : unkey sath sath hum par bhi (rahmaten aur barkaten nazil farma). Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye hadees bhi hamarey ustaade-Giraami (Qaasim bin Zakariya) ney apni kitab sey dekh kar bayan ki thi magar uski sanad ghalat hai."
1289,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, wo kehtey hain : hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap par salam to hum jaan chukey hain lekin aap par durood kaisey hai? aap ney farmaya : tum kaho : (للھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد … … … حمید مجید),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par khususi rehmat nazil farma jaisey tu ney Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) aur un ki aal par rehmat nazil farmaee. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai. aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par barkaten nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) aur un ki aal par nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai. (raawi) Abdur-Rehman ney kaha : hum ye bhi kehtey they : aur unkey sath sath hum par bhi (rahmatein aur barkaten nazil farma). Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman (Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye sanad pehli sanad key muqabley mein ziyada durust hai. hum nahin jantey ke Hazrat Qasim key ilawa kisi ney is hadees mein Amr bin Murra ka zikr kiya ho.(واللہ أعلم)"
1290,"Hazrat ibne Abi Lailaa sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) ney mujh sey farmaya : main tujhey tohfa na dun? (aur wo ye hai ke) hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap par salam padhna to hum jaan chukey hain lekin aap par durood kaisey padhen? aap ney farmaya : tum kaho (للھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد … … … حمید مجید),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par khususi rahmatein nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par rahmatein nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai. aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par barkaten nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par barkaten nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai.''"
1291,"Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap par durood kaisey padha jaey? aap ney farmaya : tum kaho : (للھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد … … … حمید مجید),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par khususi rahmatein nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) aur un ki aal par rahmatein nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai. aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par barkaten nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) aur un ki aal par barkaten nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai."
1292,"Hazrat Talha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur kehney laga : aey Allah key Nabi ! hum aap par durood kaisey padhein? aap ney farmaya : tum kaho : (للھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد … … … حمید مجید),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par khususi rehmat nazil farma jaisey tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par rehmat nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai. aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki aal par barkaten nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par barkaten nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai.''"
1293,"Hazrat Musa bin Talha bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Zaid bin Khaarija (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey puchha tha to aap ney farmaya tha : mujh par durood padho aur khub koshish sey dua karo aur kaho : (اللھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد و Ali (Raziallahu anhu) آل محمد),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aale Muhammad par khususi rahmatein nazil farma."
1294,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, wo farmatey hain : hamney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap par salam padhna to hamney jaan liya hai magar aap par durood kaisey hai? aap ney farmaya : tum kaho (اللھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد عبدک … … … Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ابراھیم),''aey Allah ! apney bandey aur Rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par khususi rehmat nazil farma, jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par rehmat nazil farmaee. aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) par barkat nazil farma jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) par barkat nazil farmaee."
1295,"Hazrat Abu-Humed Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, logon ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum aap par durood kaisey padhein? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum yun kaho : (لھم ! صل Ali (Raziallahu anhu) محمد و ازواجہ و ذریتہ),''aey Allah ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aap ki biwiyon aur aap ki nasal par rahmatein nazil farma.''Haris ki hadees mein ye lafz bhi hain : (کما صلیت … … … و ذریتہ),''jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par rahmatein nazil farmaeen aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam), aap ki biwiyon aur aap ki nasal par barkaten nazil farma.'' yahan sey phir dono raawi muttafiq hain : (کما بارکت … … … حمید مجید),''jis tarah tu ney Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ki aal par barkaten nazil farmaeen. yaqinan to tareef aur buzurgi wala hai.'' Imam Abu Abdur-Rehman Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke hamein ye hadees Hazrat Quteba ney do dafa bayan farmaee. malum yun hota hai ke un sey eik line reh gaee."
1296,"Hazrat Abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) eik din aaye to aap key chehrey par khushi key aasaar nazar aa rahey they. (hamarey istifsaar par) aap ney farmaya : Jibril merey paas aaye aur kehney lagey : aey Muhammad ! kya aap key liye ye baat khush kun nahin hai ke aap ki ummat mein sey jo shakhs bhi aap par durood padheyga, main is par das baar rehmat utaaroonga aur aap ki ummat mein sey jo shakhs bhi aap par salam padheyga, main is par das dafa salam nazil karunga."
1297,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera sey marwi (riwayat hui) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs mujh par eik dafa durood padheyga Allah Taala is par das dafa rehmat nazil farmaeyga."
1298,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs mujh par eik dafa durood padheyga, Allah Taala is par das rahmatein nazil farmaeyga aur uski das ghaltiyaan maaf kar di jaeyngi aur uskey das darjey buland kiye jaeyngey."
1299,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab hum namaz mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey (tashahud mein) bethtey they to hum kehtey they : Allah key bandon ki taraf sey Allah Taala par salam ho, falan par salam aur falan par salam. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum (السلام Ali (Raziallahu anhu) اللہ) na kaho kyonkey Allah Taala to khud salam hai balke jab tum mein sey koi shakhs (qaaedey mein) bethey to wo kahe : (التحیات للہ … … … ورسولہ),''tamam aadaab (qauli ibaadaten) aur tamam duayen (qauli ibaadaten) aur tamam achchhey kalimaat (maali ibaadaten) Allah Taala key liye hain. aey Nabi ! aap par salam ho aur Allah Taala ki rehmat aur barkaten hon. hum par aur Allah Taala key nek bandon par bhi salam ho.''jab tum ye alfaz kahogey to ye salam aur dua aasman aur zamin mein Allah Taala key har nek bandey ko pahunch jaeyngi. ''main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala key siwa koi (haqeeqi) mabood nahin. aur main gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Allah Taala key bandey aur Rasool hain.''phir iskey baad (durood padh kar) jo (manqul) dua usey ziyada pasand ho, muntakhab karey aur padhey."
1300,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Hazrat Ummey Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aayin aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! mujhey kuchh aisey kalmiaat sikha dijiye jin key sath main namaz mein dua kiya karun. aap ney farmaya : das dafa (Subhan Allah) padha kar aur das dafa (Alhamdulillah) padha kar aur das dafa (Allahu-Akbar) padha kar. phir Allah sey apni hajat talab kar. Allah Taala farmaeyga : haan ! haan ! (mainey teri hajat qubul ki)."
1301,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath betha tha aur eik aadmi khada namaz padh raha tha. jab us ney rukoo aur sajda kar liya aur tashahud bhi padh liya to us ney dua ki aur apni dua mein kaha : (اللھم ! انی اسئلک بان لک الحمد … … … الخ), ''aey Allah ! main tujh sey sawal karta hun is bina par ke terey liye hi tareef hai. terey siwa koi (haqeeqi) mabood nahin. to bahut ehsan karney wala hai. aasmano aur zaminon ko bila mada paida karney wala hai. aey buzurgi aur izzat waley ! aey zinda aur Javed ! aey sab ko qaaim rakhney waley ! be-shak main tujh sey sawal karta hun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney apney sahaba sey farmaya : tum jantey ho us ney kin lafzon sey dua ki? unhoney kaha : Allah Taala aur us ka Rasool ba-khoobi jantey hain. aap ney farmaya is zaat ki qism jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! us ney Allah Taala key us Azeem naam key sath dua ki hai ke jab uskey sath Allah ko pukara jaey to wo zarur jawab deta hai aur jab uskey sath kuchh manga jaey to zarur ata farmata hai."
1302,"Hazrat «Mihjan» bin Adraa bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein dakhil huye jab ke eik aadmi apni namaz mukammal kar chuka tha aur tashahud ki haalat mein tha. us ney kaha : (اللھم ! انی اسئلک یا اللہ ! _ _ _ الغفور الرحیم) aey Allah! main tujh sey sawal karta hun us bina par ke to wahid hai. yakta aur be niaz hai, jisney na kisi ko jana aur na wo jana gaya, aur na koi us ka hamsar hai, ke to merey gunah maaf farma dey. bilashuba tu hi bahut ziyada bakhshney wala, nihayat reham karney wala hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen martaba farmaya : tehqiq usey maaf kar diya gaya."
1303,"Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey guzarish ki ke mujhey koi aisi dua sikha dijiye jo main apni namaz mein karun. aap ney farmaya : yun kaha karo : ( اللھم ! انی zulmat … … … الرحیم ) aey Allah ! mainey apni jaan par bahut ziyada zulm kya hai aur terey siwa koi gunah maaf nahin kar sakta, lihaza merey liye apni taraf sey bakhshish farma aur mujh par reham farma. bilashuba tu hi bahut ziyada maaf karney wala, nihayat reham karney wala hai."
1304,Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney mera haath pakda aur farmaya : aey Muaz ! main tujh sey mohabbat karta hun. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main bhi aap sey mohabbat karta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : phir to kisi namaz mein ye dua karna na chhod : (رب أعنی Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ذکرک … …) aey merey rab ! meri madad farma ke main tera zikr karun aur tera shukr karun aur teri ibadat achi tarah bana sanwar key karun.
1305,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni namaz mein ye dua padhtey they : (اللھم إنی أسئلک التثبت … … … لما تعلم),''aey Allah ! main tujh sey sawal karta hun ke main Deen key mamley mein sabit qadam rahun aur hidayat key husool mein pur-azm rahun aur main tujh sey sawal karta hun ke teri nematon ka shukar ada karun aur teri ibadat achchhey tareeqey sey karun aur main tujh sey qalbe-sulaim aur sachchi zaban maangta hun. aur tujh sey main har us chiz ki khair maangta hun jo to janta hai aur har us chiz key shar sey teri panah chahta hun jo to janta hai aur tujh sey har us gunah ki maafi maangta hun jo to janta hai."
1306,"Hazrat Saaib bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ammaar bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) ney hamein eik namaz padhaai aur badi mukhtasar padhaai. kuchh logon ney un sey kaha ke aap ney badi halki aur mukhtasar namaz padhaai hai. aap kehney lagey : iskey bawajud mainey namaz mein bahut si duayen padhi hain jo mainey Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey sunin. jab wo uthey to eik aadmi unkey peechhey chala … … … wo khud Hazrat Saaib hi they, lekin unhoney apna naam poshida rakha … … … aur un sey wo duayen poochin. phir wapis aa kar us ney logon ko bataeen. (eik dua ye thi : ) (اللھم ! بعلمک الغیب … … … واجعلنا ھداۃ مھتدین), ''aey Allah ! chunkey to ilme-ghaib janta hai aur tamam makhluqat par qudrat rakhta hai, is liye (main tujh sey sawal karta hun ke) to mujhey us waqt tak zinda rakh jab tak merey liye zinda rehna behtar hai aur mujhey us waqt faut kar dena jab merey liye wafat behtar samjhey. aur aey Allah ! main tujh sey chhipey taur par aur zaahiran terey dar ka sawal karta hun aur raza mandi aur narazi har haal mein sachchi aur hikmat bhari baat kehney ka sawal karta hun. aur ameeri aur faqeeri mein darmiyaanaa rawiyaa ikhtiyar karney ki tofiq maangta hun aur tujh sey aisi nematon ka sawal karta hun jo kabhi khatam na hon. aur aisi aankh ki thandak (khushi aur lazzat) maangta hun jo kabhi munqata' (khatm) na ho. aur faislon par razi rehney ka sawal karta hun. aur maut key baad lazeez zindagi maangta hun. aur terey roey aqdas key deedar key mazey aur teri mulaqat key shoq ka talabgar hun, baghair iskey ke kisi nuqsandeh musibat mein phansun ya kisi gumrah-kun fitney mein mubtala hun. aey Allah ! hamein eman ki zeenat sey aarasta farma aur hamein hidayat-yafta (aur gumrahon ko) raah dikhlaane wala bana dey."
1307,"Hazrat Qais bin Ibaad bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Ammaar bin Yaasir (Raziallahu anhu) ney logon ko halki namaz padhaai. goya ke logon ney usey ajeeb samjha. aap ney farmaya : kya mainey rukoo aur sajdey mukammal nahin kiye? logon ney kaha : kyon nahin (woh to theek hain.) aap ney farmaya : mainey namaz mein wo dua padhi hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz mein padha kartey they : (اللھم بعلمک الغیب … … … ھداۃ مھتدین),''aey Allah ! chunkey to ghaib janta hai aur makhluq par qudrate-kaamila rakhta hai, lihaza (main tujh sey sawal karta hun ke) to mujhey itni der tak zinda rakh jab tak zindagi merey liye behtar ho aur us waqt faut kar dena jab to merey liye wafat behtar samjhey. main tujh sey khilwat (tanhaai) aur jalat (mehfil) mein tera dar maangta hun aur raza-mandi aur narazi mein kalimae-haq kehney ki tofiq maangta hun. aur tujh sey wo nemat maangta hun jo khatam na ho aur aankh ki wo thandak (lazzat aur suroor) jo kabhi munqata' (khatm) na ho aur taqdir par razi rehney, maut key baad pur-suroor zindagi aur terey roey-aqdas ki ziyaarat ki lazzat aur teri mulaqat ka shoq maangta hun aur har nuqsan-deh musibat aur har gumrahkun fitney sey teri panah talab karta hun. aey Allah ! hamein eman ki zeenat sey muzayyan farma (sawaanr dey) aur hamein hidayat-yafta (aur gumrahon key liye) raah dikhlaaney wala (raahnuma) bana dey."
1308,"Hazrat Fardaa bin Naufal bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey kaha : mujhey koi aisi chiz bayan kijiye jis key sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni namaz mein dua farmaya kartey they. unhoney kaha : zarur, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) yun padha kartey they : (اللھم ! انی عوذبک من شرما عملت ومن شرما لم أعمل),''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun un burey kamon key shar sey jo mainey kiye aur jo abhi nahin kiye.''"
1309,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey qabr key azab key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : han, azabe-qabr bar-haq hai. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke iskey baad mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko jo bhi namaz padhtey dekha, aap is mein azabe-qabr sey panah maangtey they."
1310,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz mein ye dua padhtey they : (اللھم ! إنی أعوذبک من عذاب القبر … … … والمغرم),''aey Allah ! main qabr key azab sey teri panah chahta hun aur Masih Dajjaal key fitne aur aazmaaish sey teri panah chahta hun aur zindagi aur maut key fitney sey teri panah chahta hun aur aey Allah ! main gunah aur qarz (ya gunahon key bojh) sey teri panah chahta hun.'' kisi kehney waley ney aap sey kaha : aap qarz sey kis qadr ziyada panah talab kartey hain ! aap ney farmaya : jab koi aadmi maqrooz ho jata hai, phir baat karta hai to jhoot boltaa hai aur wada karta hai to wada khilafi karta hai."
1311,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi namazi tashahud padh chukey to in chaar chizon sey Allah Taala ki panah talab karey : jahannam key azab, qabr key azab, zindagi aur maut ki aazmaaish aur Masih Dajjaal key shar sey, phir iskey baad (manqul (naqal hui) duaon mein sey) apney liye apni pasandida dua kerey."
1312,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni namaz mein tashahud key baad ye alfaz kehtey they : (وأحسن الکلام کلام اللہ و أحسن الھدی ھدی محمد ﷺ),''sab sey behtareen kalamullah Taala ka kalam hai aur sab sey achchhaa tariqa Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ka tariqa hai.''"
1313,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney eik aadmi ko naqis namaz padhtey dekha. Hazrat Huzefa ney us sey puchha : to kitney arsey sey aisi namaz padh raha hai? us ney kaha : chaalis saal sey. aap ney farmaya : yaqin kar chaalis saal sey tu ney namaz padhi hi nahin aur agar to isi qisam ki namaz padhta padhta mar jata to Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key Deen par faut na hota. phir aap kehney lagey : bilashuba insan halki namaz padhney key bawajud mukammal aur achchhey tareeqey sey namaz padh sakta hai."
1314,"eik Badri Sahabi (Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafey ) Raziallahu anhu ney bayan kiya ke eik aadmi masjid mein dakhil huwa aur namaz padhney laga aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey ba-ghaur dekhney lagey. hamein is baat ka pata nahin tha. jab wo namaz sey farigh huwa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf aaya aur salam kaha. aap ney farmaya : wapis ja, dobara namaz padh, tu ney namaz nahin padhi. wo wapis gaya aur dobara namaz padhi, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya. aap ney phir farmaya : wapis ja, phir namaz padh, tu ney namaz nahin padhi. do teen dafa aisa hi huwa. aakhir wo aadmi kehney laga : aey Allah key Rasool ! qism us zaat ki jisney aap ko izzat bakhshi ! main to (bar-bar namaz padh kar) thak gaya hun, lihaza mujhey sikha dijiye. aap ney farmaya : jab to namaz key iraday sey khada ho to wuzu kar aur achchhi tarah wuzu kar, phir qibley ki taraf munh kar aur (Allahu-Akbar) keh, phir qirat kar, phir rukoo kar aur itminan sey rukoo kar, phir sar utha yahan tak ke sidha khada ho jaey, phir sajda kar yahan tak ke itminan sey sajda kerey. phir sar utha yahan tak ke to itminan sey beth jaey, phir sajda kar yahan tak ke itminan sey sajda kerey. phir sar utha, phir (har rakat mein) aisey hi kar yahan tak ke to apni namaz sey farigh ho jaey."
1315,"eik Badri sahabi (Hazrat Rifaa bin Raafey ) (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath masjid mein betha tha ke eik aadmi dakhil huwa aur us ney do rakatein padhin, phir wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap ko salam kaha jab ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) usey namaz mein dekhtey rahey they. aap ney usey salam ka jawab diya aur farmaya : wapis ja 'dobara namaz padh' tu ney namaz nahin padhi. wo wapis gaya, phir namaz padhi, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaya aur aap ko salam kaha. aap ney usey salam ka jawab diya aur farmaya : wapis ja 'phir namaz padh' tu ney namaz nahin padhi. yahan tak ke teesri ya chauthi dafa hui to usney kaha : qism us zaat ki jisney aap par kitab utaari ! main to (bar-bar namaz padh kar) thak gaya hun. meri khahish hai ke aap mujhey (namaz padh kar) dikhayen aur mujhey sikhlaa-den. aap ney farmaya : jab to namaz ka irada karey to wuzu kar aur behtareen wuzu kar, phir qibley ki taraf munh kar aur (Allahu-Akbar) keh, phir Quran (kam se kam Faatiha) padh, phir rukoo kar yahan tak ke tujhey rukoo mein itminan hasil ho, phir sar utha yahan tak ke sidha khada ho jaey, phir sajda kar yahan tak ke tujhey sajdey mein itminan hasil ho, phir sar utha yahan tak ke to itminan sey beth jaey, phir doosra sajda kar yahan tak ke tujhey sajdey mein itminan hasil ho, phir sar utha, phir jab to is tareeqey sey namaz mukammal kar ley to teri namaz mukammal aur sahih ho jaeygi. aur jo to in kamon mein kami kerega to yaqinan apni namaz hi mein naqs daleyga."
1316,"Hazrat Saad bin Hisham bayan farmatey hain ke mainey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey kaha : aey Ummul-Mominin ! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key witr (raat ki nafl namaz) key barey mein bataiye. unhoney farmaya : hum aap key liye aap ki miswak aur wuzu ka pani tayyar kar key rakh detey they. jab Allah Taala chahta aap ko jagaata. aap uth kar miswak kartey, wuzu farmatey aur aath rakaat padhtey un mein aap tashahud key liye nahin bethtey they magar aathwin rakat key baad. phir Allah Taala ka zikr farmatey aur duayen padhtey phir itni aawaz sey salam kehtey ke hum sun letey."
1317,Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ( namaz key aakhir mein) daeyn baeyn (munh modtey they aur) salam kehtey they.
1318,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekhta tha ke aap ( namaz key ikhtitaam par) daeyn aur baeyn salam kehtey they aur is qadr munh modtey they ke aap key rukhsaar at'har ki safedi nazar aaney lagti thi. Imam abu-Abdur-Rehman ( Nasai) (Rahmatullahi Alaih) bayan kartey hain ke ye ( Hadees key raawi ) Abdullah bin Jafar motabar raawi hain, albatta Ali bin Madini key walid Abdullah bin Jafar bin «Najeeh» matrook hain. (unki hadees moatabar nahin hai.)"
1319,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke (ibtida (shuruat) mein) jab hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechey namaz padhtey they to hum ( السلام علیکم , السلام علیکم ) kehtey aur sath haathon ko bhi daeyn baain uthatey they. ( yani daeyn taraf salam key waqt daeyn taraf aur baain taraf salam key waqt baain taraf haath uthatey . ) aap ney ( dekha to) farmaya : unhein kya hai ke apney haathon sey (daeyn baeyn) isharay kartey hain jaisey sarkash ghodon ki dumein hain. kya ye kafi nahin ke namazi apney haath apni raan hi par rakhey aur zaban sey apney daeyn aur baeyn apney sathiyon ko salam keh dey."
1320,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap har jhuktey, uthtey aur khadey hotey aur bethtey waqt « Allahu-akbar » kehtey aur apney daeyn aur baain salam kehtey : ( السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ , السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ ) tum par Allah Taala ka salam aur rehmat ho. (aur munh bhi modtey they ) yahan tak ke aap key rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aati thi aur mainey Hazrat abu-Bakar o umr Raziallahu anhuma ko bhi aisey kartey dekha hai."
1321,"Hazrat Waasey bin Hibban ney Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz key barey mein puchha to unhoney farmaya : aap jab jhuktey they to « Allahu-akbar » kehtey they aur jab sar uthatey they, tab bhi « Allahu-akbar » kehtey they. phir (namaz key ikhtitaam par) daeyn taraf munh kar key kehtey : ( السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ ) aur baain taraf munh kar key kehtey : ( السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ )"
1322,Hazrat Waasey bin Hibban sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma sey kaha : mujhey bataiye ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz kaisey hoti thi ? aap ney zikr kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) « Allahu-akbar » kehtey they aur ( namaz key ikhtitaam par) daeyn taraf « السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ » kehtey they aur baain taraf « السلام علیکم » kehtey they.
1323,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke goya main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key rukhsaar ki safedi ko dekh raha hun, aap apni daain taraf farmatey : ( السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ ) aur baain taraf farmatey : ( السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ )."
1324,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) daain taraf salam phertey yahan tak ke aap key rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aati, phir baain taraf yahan tak ke aap key rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aati."
1325,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni daain aur baain taraf salam phertey (aur kehtey :) ( السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ , السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ ) yahan tak ke daain taraf bhi aap key rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aati aur baain taraf bhi aap key rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aati."
1326,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni daain taraf salam phertey (aur kehtey) : ( السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ ) yahan tak ke aap key daeyn rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aati, phir baain taraf salam phertey (aur kehtey :) ( السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ السلام علیکم و رحمۃ اللہ ) yahan tak ke aap key baeyn rukhsaar ki safedi nazar aati."
1327,"Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath namaz padhi. jab hum salam phertey they to haathon key sath bhi ishara kartey aur kehtey ( السلام علیکم , السلام علیکم ) hamen Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney dekh liya to aap ney farmaya : tumhein kya huwa ke tum apney haathon sey isharay kartey ho jaisey ye sarkash ghodon ki dumein hain. jab tum mein sey koi aadmi ( namaz key aakhir mein) salam kahey to apney sathi ki taraf munh modey. haath sey ishara na kerey."
1328,"Hazrat Utban bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main apni qom banu-Sulem ko namaz padhaya karta tha. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huwa aur arz kya ke main taqriban na-beena ho chuka hun. (barsat key mausam mein) barishi aur selabi pani merey aur meri qom ki masjid key darmiyan rukawat ban jata hai, is liye main chahta hun ke aap tashrif laeyn aur merey ghar mein kisi jagah namaz ada farmaain jisey mein ( gharelu ) masjid bana lun. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : insha Allah main an-qareeb aaunga. agley din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) merey paas tashrif laye. Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap key sath they. din kafi ooncha aa chuka tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney ijazat talab ki. mainey ijazat de di. aap bethey nahin balke farmaya : tum kis jagah chahtey ho ke main namaz padhun ? mainey us jagah ki taraf ishara kya jahan mein chahta tha ke aap namaz padhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey huye, hamney aap key peechey saf bandi ki, (aap ney namaz ada ki ) phir aap ney salam phera aur aap key salam phertey hi hamney bhi salam pher diya."
1329,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) Isha ki namaz sey farigh honey key baad Fajr key tulu honey tak giyara rakat padhtey they aur un mein sey eik rakat alag ( salam sey) padhtey aur itna lamba sajda kartey ke aap key sar uthaney sey pehley tum mein sey koi shakhs pachas (50) aayaat padh sakta tha. (ibne-Wahab farmatey hain) baaz raawi baaz ki nisbat (kuch) izaafey key sath ye hadees bayan kartey hain. ye hadees mukhtasar hai.
1330,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney (bhool kar) salam pher diya, phir kuch baaten kin, phir aap ney sahw key do sajdey kiye."
1331,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney salam phera, phir bethey-bethey sahw key do sajdey kiye, phir salam phera. (Imam Nasai (Rahmatullahi Alaih) ney ) farmaya : zul-yadain ki hadees mein bhi uska zikr hai."
1332,"Hazrat Imran bin Husein Raziallahu anhuma sey marwi hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney teen rakaaton key baad salam pher diya. Hazrat kharbaq (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aap ney teen rakatein padhi hain. aap ney unhein baqiya rakat padhaai, phir salam phera, phir saho key do sajdey kiye, phir salam phera."
1333,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz ki haalat mein b-ghaur dekha to mainey aap key qiyam, rukoo, rukoo key baad sidha khada hona, sajda, do sajdon key darmiyan bethna, phir doosra sajda karna, phir salam pherney aur muqtadiyon ki taraf munh pherney key darmiyan ( qibla rukh ) bethna, taqriban barabar paya."
1334,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key daur mein aurten namaz sey salam phertey hi uth kar chali jati thin jab ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) aur aap key sath namaz padhney waley mard namazi, jab tak Allah Taala chahta (kafi der tak) bethey rehtey. phir jab Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) uthtey to mard bhi uth kar chaley jatey."
1335,"Hazrat Yazid bin Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath subh ki namaz padhi, jab aap namaz padh chukey to aap ney apna rukh (qibley sey) mod liya."
1336,Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki namaz ka ikhtitaam logon key « Allahu-akbar » kehney sey malum karta tha.
1337,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hukm diya ke main har ( farz ) namaz key baad muawwizaat padhun.
1338,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key azad karda ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab apni namaz sey farigh hotey to teen dafa ( استغفراللہ ) main Allah Taala sey bakhshish talab karta hun. padhtey aur ye dua padhtey : اللھم أنت السلام … … … والا کرام aey Allah ! to salam hai. teri hi taraf sey salamti milti hai. aey ehtiraam o izzat waley ! to ba-barkat hai.
1339,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab salam phertey to yun farmatey : اللھم أنت السلام … … … والا کرام aey Allah ! to salam hai aur tujhi sey salamti milti hai. aey ehtiraam o izzat waley! to ba-barkat hai.
1340,"Hazrat abu-Zubair bayan kartey hain ke mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anha) ko us member (member kaaba) par bayan kartey huye suna, wo farma rahey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab salam phertey to yun farmatey : لا الہ الا اللہ _ _ _ ولو کرہ الکافرون Allah taala key siwa koi mabood nahin. wo yakta hai. us ka koi shareek nahin. usi key liye badshahi hai aur usi key liye kul hamd hai. aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai. gunah sey bachney ki taqat aur neki karney ki quwat Allah ki madad key baghair hasil nahin ho sakti. Allah Taala key siwa koi (haqeeqi) mabood nahin. hum uskey siwa kisi ki ibadat nahin kartey. aey nemat, Fazal aur achi tareef waley! Allah Taala key siwa koi mabood nahin. hum khalis usi ki itaat kartey hain. chahey kafir bura hi samjhen."
1341,"Hazrat abu-Zubair bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anha) (farz) namaz key baad is tarah tahleel padhtey they : لا الہ الا اللہ _ _ _ ولو کرہ الکافرون Allah taala key siwa koi ( haqeeqi ) mabood nahin. wo yaktaa hai. us ka koi shareek nahin. usi key liye hukumat aur badshahi hai aur usi key liye har tareef hai aur wo har chiz par khub qudrat rakhney wala hai. Allah Taala key siwa koi ( haqeeqi ) mabood nahin. hum uskey siwa kisi ki ibadat nahin kartey. usi ki hain sab nematon aur usi key hain sab ehsan o Fazal aur usi key liye hain achi tareefen. Allah Taala key siwa koi (haqeeqi) mabood nahin. hum khalis usi ki itaat kartey hain, chahey kafir bura hi samjhen. phir Hazrat ibn Zuber (Raziallahu anha) farmatey they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz key baad in kalmaat key sath tahleel padhtey they."
1342,Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) key kaatib Hazrat Warraad ney bayan kya ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha : mujhey kisi aisi chiz ki khabar dijiye jo aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni ho. to unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab namaz mukammal farma letey to yun padhtey : لا الہ الا اللہ … … … منک الجد Allah taala key siwa koi ( haqeeqi ) mabood nahin. wo yakta hai. koi us ka shareek nahin. usi key liye hai badshahi aur tamam tareefen aur wo har chiz par khub qudrat rakhney wala hai. aey Allah ! nahin koi rokney wala us chiz ko jo to dey aur na koi us chiz ko ata karney wala hai jo to na dey aur kisi sahibe-haisiyat ko uski haisiyat terey muqabley mein mufeed nahin.
1343,Hazrat Warraad sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey salam pher kar yun padhtey : لا الہ الا اللہ … … … منک الجد Allah taala key siwa koi ( haqeeqi ) mabood nahin. wo yakta hai. uska koi shareek nahin. usi key liye hai badshahi aur usi key liye hai sab tareef aur wo har chiz par khub qudrat rakhney wala hai. aey Allah! koi us chiz ko rokney wala nahin jo to dey aur na koi wo chiz deney wala hai jo to rok dey aur kisi sahibe-haisiyat ko uski haisiyat terey muqabley mein mufeed nahin.
1344,Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) key kaatib Warraad sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ney Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha ke mujhey eik aisi hadees likh dijiye jo aap ney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey suni ho to Hazrat Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ney unhein likha : tehqiq mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko namaz sey farigh honey key waqt ye padhtey suna hai : [ la Ilaah illallah … … … ] padhi. Allah Taala key siwa koi ( haqeeqi) mabud nahin. wo yakta hai. uska koi shareek nahin. usi key liye badshahi hai aur usi key liye hamd hai aur wo har chiz par khub qadir hai. aap ye zikr teen dafa padhtey
1345,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi majlis mein bethtey ya namaz sey farigh hotey to kuch kalmaat padhtey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ney aap sey un kalmaat key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : agar kisi shakhs ney (us majlis mein) achi baaten ki hongi to ye kalimat qiyamat tak key liye un baaton key liye mehar ban jaeyngey aur agar us ney aur qism ki (ghalat ya fuzul ) baaten ki hongi to ye uskey liye kaffara (gunah mitaaney waley) ban jaeyngey. (aur wo kalmaat ye hain) ( سبحانک اللھم ! o بحمدک استغفرک o أتوب إلیک ) aey Allah ! to har qism key naqs o aeb sey pak hai aur tamam taarifon aur khubiyon wala hai. mein tujh sey maafi talab karta hun aur teri taraf ruju karta hun. ( yani har qism ki ghalati sey tauba karta hun. )
1346,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke eik Yahudi aurat merey paas aai aur kehney lagi ke peshab key chheentey padney sey qabr mein azab hota hai. mainey kaha : to ghalat kehti hai. us ney kaha : nahin, balke sach hai. hum peshab key chheentey padney sey chamda aur kapda kaat-tey they. (usi doran mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) namaz key liye nikley to hum unchi-unchi bol rahi thin. aap ney farmaya : kya huwa? mainey aap sey baat bayan ki. aap ney farmaya : ye sahih kehti hai. us din key baad aap ney jab bhi namaz padhi to namaz key baad ye dua zarur padhi : رب جبریل و میکائیل و إسرافیل أعذنی من حر النار و عذاب القبر aey Jibril, Mekael aur Israafil key rab ! mujhey aag ki tapish aur qabr key azab sey bacha ."
1347,"Hazrat Abu-Marwaan sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat Kaab ney mujh sey qism kha kar kaha : qism us zaat ki jisney Hazrat Musa alehissalam key liye samandar ko phaad kar raastey banaey ! hum Torat mein ye likha paatey hain ke Allah key Nabi Hazrat Dawud alehissalam jab namaz sey farigh hotey they to yun kehtey they : (اللھم ! اصلح لی … … منک الجد),''aey Allah ! merey liye merey Deen ko durust farma jisey tu ney merey liye (duniya aur aakhirat mein ruswai sey) bachao ka zariya banaya hai. aur merey liye meri duniya ko durust farma jisey tu ney merey liye zindagi guzarney ka sabab banaya hai. aey Allah ! main teri narazi sey bachney key liye teri raza mandi ki panah chahta hun aur teri saza sey bachney key liye teri maafi ki panah chahta hun aur terey ghazab sey bachney key liye teri rehmat ki panah chahta hun. jo chiz to dey, usey koi rokney wala nahin aur jo chiz to rok ley, usey koi deney wala nahin aur kisi maal waley ko terey yahaan maal faaeeda nahin deta (balke amal faeyda deta hai). Hazrat Kaab ney kaha : mujhey Hazrat Suheb (Raziallahu anhu) ney bataya ke Hazrat Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi namaz sey faraaghat key waqt ye kalimaat kaha kartey they."
1348,"Hazrat Muslim bin Abu-Bakra sey manqul hai ke merey walid mohtaram har namaz key baad ye padha kartey they : (اللھم ! انی اعوذبک من الکفر و الفقر وعذاب القبر),''aey Allah ! main kufr, faqr aur azabe-qabr sey teri panah chahta hun.''to main bhi ye kalimaat kehney laga. walid mohtaram poochhney lagey : beta ! ye kalimaat kis sey seekhey hain? mainey kaha : aap sey. unhoney farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) bhi namaz key baad ye kalimaat kaha kartey they."
1349,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : do kaam aisey hain ke jo musalman bhi un par pabandi kerey. wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. ye dono kaam bahut aasan hain aur in par amal karney waley bahut kam hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : (woh do kaam ye hain : ) paanch farz namazon mein sey har farz namaz key baad das dafa (Subhan Allah) padhey, das dafa (Alhamdulillah) padhey aur das dafa (Allahu-Akbar) padhey. is tarah zaban par (padhney mein) ye kul dedh-sau kalimaat hain magar meezaan (taraazu) mein (sawab key lihaz sey) dedh hazar hain. (kyonkey har neki key badley mein Allah Taala das guna jaza deta hai). mainey dekha, Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) in kalimaat ko haath sey shumar kartey they. (doosra kaam ye hai ke) jab tum mein sey koi shakhs apney bistar ya charpai par letey to tentees dafa (Subhan Allah) padhey, tentees dafa (Alhamdulillah) padhey aur chauntees dafa (Allahu-Akbar) padhey. ye zaban par (padhney key lihaz sey) sau kalimaat hain aur meezaan mein (sawab key lihaz sey) eik hazar hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum mein sey kon aisa shakhs hai jo har din raat mein do hazar paanch-sau gunah karta hai? puchha gaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! eik aadmi un do kamon ki pabandi kaisey nahin kar sakta? aap ney farmaya : jab koi aadmi namaz mein hota hai to shetan uskey paas aa kar kehta hai, falan chiz yad kar, falan chiz yad kar (is tarah uski tawajjoh idhar-udhar ho jati hai aur wo namaz key fauran baad uth kar chala jata hai). isi tarah sotey waqt bhi shetan aa kar (idhar-udhar key khayalat mein phansa deta hai aur) usey sulaa deta hai(usey us zikr ki taraf tawajjoh hi nahin hoti)."
1350,"Hazrat Kaab bin Ajra (Raziallahu anhu) sey marwi hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : farz namazon key baad padhey janey waley kuchh aisey kalimaat hain jinhein padhney wala kabhi nakam nahin hota. har namaz key baad tentees dafa (Subhan Allah), tentees dafa (Alhamdulillah) aur chauntees dafa (Allahu-Akbar) padhey."
1351,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke logon ko hukm diya gaya ke har farz namaz key baad tentees dafa (Subhan Allah), tentees dafa (Alhamdulillah) aur chauntees dafa (Allahu-Akbar) kahen. eik Ansari sahabi ko khuwab aaya. usey kaha gaya : tumhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) neu hukm diya hai ke tum har namaz key baad tentees dafa (Subhan Allah), tentees dafa (Alhamdulillah) aur chauntees dafa (Allahu-Akbar) kaho? us ney kaha : haan. khuwab mein nazar aaney waley shakhs ney kaha : tum unhein pachchees dafa kar lo aur un mein (La-Ilaah-illa-Allah) ka izafa kar lo. jab subah hui to wo Ansari Sahabi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas hazir huye aur pura khuwab bayan kiya. aap ney farmaya : aisey kar lo."
1352,"Hazrat ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke eik Sahabi ney khuwab mein dekha. un sey puchha gaya : tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney tumhein kis chiz ka hukm diya hai? unhoney kaha : aap ney hamein hukm diya hai ke hum (farz namaz key baad) tentees dafa (Subhan Allah), tentees dafa (Alhamdulillah) aur chauntees dafa (Allahu-Akbar) kahen. ye eik sau ho jaeyngey. us ney kaha : tum pachchees dafa (Subhan Allah), pachchees dafa (Alhamdulillah), pachchees dafa (Allahu-Akbar) aur pachchees dafa (La Ilaah illa Allah) padh liya karo. ye bhi eik sau ho jaeyngey. jab subah hui to us Sahabi ney ye khuwab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan kiya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jaisey ye Ansari kehta hai, isi tarah kar lo."
1353,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) apni biwi mohtarma Juweriya binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) key paas sey guzrey jab ke wo apni jaaey-namaz par bethi zikr azkaar kar rahi thin. phir aap dophare key qarib dobara unkey paas sey guzrey. (woh us waqt bhi bethi thin) aap ney un sey farmaya : tum us waqt sey isi haalat mein ho? unhoney kaha : ji haan. aap ney farmaya : main tumhein kuchh kalimaat na sikha dun jinhein tum padha karo : (Subhan Allah adad khilqa) Allah ki tasbih hai, uski makhluqat ki tadaad key barabar. teen dafa (Subhan Allah raza nafsa) Allah ki tasbih hai uski raza mandi key mutabiq. teen dafa (Subhan Allah زنۃ عرشہ ) Allah ki tasbih hai uskey arsh key wazan key mutabiq. teen dafa (Subhan Allah مداد کلماتہ ) Allah ki tasbih hai uskey kalimaat ki roshnai key barabar teen dafa."
1354,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke faqir sahaba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas aaye aur arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! maaldaar log hamari tarah namazein padhtey hain aur hamari tarah rozey rakhtey hain, lekin unkey paas maal hai jis sey wo sadqa kartey hain aur ghulam azad kartey hain. (hum unkey darjey ko kaisey pahunch saktey hain)? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab tum namaz padh chuko to tentees martaba (Subhan Allah), tentees martaba (Alhamdulillah), tentees martaba (Allahu-Akbar) aur das dafa (La-Ilaah-illa-Allah) padh liya karo. tum is amal ki badolat apney sey aagey badh janey waley logon ko ja milogey aur un logon sey bahut aagey badh jaaogey jo tum sey peechhey hain (ya jo ye amal nahin kartey)."
1355,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shakhs subah ki namaz key baad sau dafa (Subhan Allah) aur sau dafa (La-Ilaah-illa-Allah) padhey, uskey sab gunah maaf ho jaeyngey agar-che wo samandar ke jhaag key barabar hon."
1356,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma bayan kartey hain ke mainey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko tasbeehaat shumar kartey dekha.
1357,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) maahe-ramzan key darmiyan waley das dino mein aetikaf bethtey they. phir jab bees raaten guzar jatin aur ikkeeswin raat aa jati to aap aur aap key sath aetikaf bethney waley gharon ko chaley jatey. phir eik saal us raat bhi aetikaf mein bethey rahey jis raat aap ghar ko lot jaya kartey they. phir aap ney logon ko khutba diya aur jo Allah ney chaha us ka unhein hukm diya. phir farmaya : main darmiyan waley das dino ka aetikaf betha karta tha. ab mujhey khayal aaya hai ke main aakhiri das dino ka bhi aetikaf bethun, isliye jo shakhs merey sath aetikaf betha hai, wo apni aetikaf gaah mein betha rahey. tehqiq mainey lailatul-qadr khuwab mein dekhi thi magar mujhey wo bhulwaa di gaee, lihaza us raat ko aakhiri das dino ki taaq raaton mein talash karo. mainey khuwab mein dekha hai ke main keechad mein sajda kar raha hun. Hazrat Abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ikkeeswin raat hi hum par barish barsi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ki sajda gaah mein masjid tapakney lagi. mainey dekha ke jab aap subah ki namaz sey farigh ho kar hamari taraf mudey to aap ka chehra (yani maatha aur naak ka kinara) keechad sey tar tha."
1358,Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Fajr ki namaz padh chuktey to suraj tulu honey tak apni namaz wali jagah mein bethey rehtey.
1359,"Hazrat Simaak bin Harab sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) sey kaha : aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key paas betha kartey they? unhoney farmaya : haan ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) jab Fajr ki namaz padh letey to suraj tulu honey tak apni namaz wali jagah mein bethey rehtey. aap key sahaba kiram Raziallahu anhum aap key samney baaten kartey rehtey. kabhi jahiliyat ki baaten zikr kartey, kabhi she'r padhtey aur hanstey. Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) muskuraatey rehtey."
1360,Hazrat Suddi sey riwayat hai ke mainey Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha ke jab main namaz sey farigh ho jaaun to kaisey uthoon? daeyn janib sey ya baain janib sey? unhoney farmaya : mainey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko umoomi taur par daeyn janib mud kar uthtey dekha hai.
1361,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke tum mein sey koi shakhs apney aap par shetan ka hissa na rakhey ke wo apney aap par zaroori qarar dey ke sirf daeyn janib hi sey mudeyga. bilashuba mainey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ko aksar baain janib sey mudte dekha hai.
1362,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke mainey dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho kar bhi pani pi letey they aur beth kar bhi. nangey paaun bhi namaz padh liya kartey they aur jootay pehan kar bhi aur namaaziyon ki taraf daeyn taraf sey bhi mud jatey they aur baain taraf sey bhi.
1363,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke aurten Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key peechhey Fajr ki namaz padhti thin. jab aap salam phertey to wo fauran uth kar chali jatin. unhoney badi chadaren lapeti hoti thin aur andherey ki wajeh sey unhein pehchana nahin ja sakta tha.
1364,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey hain ke eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein namaz padhaai, phir hamari taraf mutawajjeh huye aur farmaya : main tumhara Imam hun, lihaza rukoo, sajdey, uthney aur salam pherney mein mujh sey jaldi na kiya karo. main tumhein har haal mein dekhta hun, tum aagey ho ya peechhey. phir farmaya : qism hai us zaat ki jis key haath mein meri jaan hai ! agar tum wo cheezen dekh lo jo main dekh chuka hun to tum bahut kam hanso aur bahut ziyada rau'o. hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap ney kya dekha hai? aap ney farmaya : mainey jannat aur dozakh dekhi hai."
1365,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke hamney Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Ramzanul-Mubarak key rozey rakhey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein raat ko (taraawih ki) namaz nahin padhaai yahan tak ke maahe muqaddas key saat din baqi reh gaey to aap ney (teiswin raat ko) hamein (taraawih ki) namaz padhaai yahan tak ke raat ka taqriban teesra hissa guzar gaya. phir chaubiswin raat hui to hamein namaz nahin padhaai. jab pachchiswin raat hui to phir hamein namaz padhaai yahan tak ke taqriban nisf (aadhi) raat guzar gaee. hamney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! agar aap sari raat hamein nafl namaz padhatey rehtey to kya hi khub hota. aap ney farmaya : jab koi shakhs Imam key sath namaz padhey aur Imam key wapis janey tak sath rahey to uskey liye puri raat ka qiyam shumar kiya jata hai. phir chhabiswin raat hui to aap ney hamein nafl namaz na padhaai. jab maahe-muqaddas key teen din baqi reh gaey (yani sattaaisween raat ko) to aap ney apni betiyon aur biwiyon ko bhi bula bheja aur bahut log jama ho gaey to aap ney hamein nafl namaz padhaai yahan tak ke hamein khatra mehsus huwa ke 'falah' (sehri) reh jaeygi. phir iskey baad is maah muqaddas ki kisi raat ko hamen nafl namaz (taraawih) nahin padhaai. (Hadees key raawi ) Dawud (bin Abu Hind) ney kaha : mainey (apney ustaad Waleed sey) puchha : ""falah"" kya hai? unhoney kaha : sehri hai."
1366,"Hazrat Aqba bin Haris (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain mainey eik dafa Madina Munawra mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath Asr ki namaz padhi. namaz sey farigh hotey hi aap jaldi sey logon ki gardanen phlaangte huye ghar chaley gaey yahan tak ke logon ney aap ki jaldi par tajjub kiya. kuchh Sahaba aap key peechhey gaey. aap apni kisi biwi key ghar dakhil huye, phir bahar tashrif laye aur farmaya : mujhey Asr ki namaz key doran mein yad aaya ke kuchh sona hamarey ghar pada hai. mainey pasand na kiya ke wo raat ko hamarey ghar rahey, is liye mainey wo taqseem karney ka hukm diya hai."
1367,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) jange-khandaq key din suraj ghurub honey key baad kuffar Quraish ko bura bhala kehney lagey aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main to badi mushkil sey aen ghurub shams (suraj dubney) key qarib namaze-Asr padh saka. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah ki qism ! mainey to abhi tak namaz nahin padhi. phir hum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi Wasallam) key sath wadi Bat'haan mein gaey. aap ney bhi wuzu kiya aur hamney bhi. phir ghurub shams key baad pehley Asr ki namaz padhi, phir Maghrib ki."
